videos.description: In his last home game as a senior at Oregon State, Gary Payton II surprises his father by wearing Gary Payton Sr.'s No. 20 before facing Washington State.
videos.headline: Gary Payton II wears his father's old No. 20 as a surprise

videos.description: Oregon State's Gary Payton II is all alone on the fast break and finishes with authority on a huge left-handed dunk, causing his father to applaud.
videos.headline: Gary Payton II throws down the hammer with huge dunk

videos.description: Oregon State Seniors honored before the game on Senior Day.
videos.headline: Oregon State Seniors honored before the game on Senior Day.

videos.description: Gary Payton II continues his personal vendetta against the rim with another vicious one-hand dunk, this time going right over a Washington State defender to do so.
videos.headline: Gary Payton II just keeps dunking on everybody
